Archbishop Timothy Ndambuki of the Africa Brotherhood Church has congratulated retired Anglican Archbishop Eliud Wabukala for his appointment as the head of the EACC.In a press briefing in Machakos town yesterday, he said he has faith in Wabukala&rsquo;s ability to serve in that position.&ldquo;I know Wabukala as a straight forward man, humble and Intelligent. He has always been good in adhering to the church constitution and with a good team that respects the constitution he will be able to deliver,&rdquo; Ndambuki said.